attributes.action: Start screening every person who enters UK for Coronavirus
attributes.background: Why is there no screening for Coronavirus at the UK airports? There are other countries doing this in order to stop the spread. I strongly believe that this should be done as a matter of urgency to stop further spread into UK. The queues may be long but atleast we can identify and stop the spread
